              <h1 class="text-center">Privacy And Cookies Policy</h1>
              <p><i>Updated December 2021</i></p>          
                <p>This is the privacy statement for the Acron Group of companies. Please read it carefully. You should only use this site and complete any website forms if you agree to our use of information about you in accordance with this privacy statement.</p><br>
                <h5>Protecting your personal data</h5>
                <p>We’re committed to protecting you and your family’s personal data and information. This policy applies to any personal information or “personal data” that we collect from you. It covers how we:</p>
